description:
This is a 13 minute workout called '10MIN everyday full body hourglass pilates workout // beginner friendly //w/verbal cues | LIDIAVMERA' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
